 DPU
    Requires Schema IDs it can consume and schema IDs it can produce. (version is implicit)
    Can be a library or web service

 DVU
    Requires Schema ID(s)
    //Requires some structured data
    Requires javascript dependencies  

 Source Code Repo
 Keywords

 Organizations  -- just user 

Other things to display:
Schema IDs that can be accepted as input by DPUs and DVUs.
Primitive output schemas from DPUs

Organizations -- just user, propegate to schemas and units

Schema Changes -- Log and display 
    
Output Schema (DSU, DPU)    
Input Schema (DPU, DVU)
